In short, Haning is a really, really talented artist. Her confident, her passion in art have helped  her to in someway overcome her dark past bit by bit.

Hopefully, with the support from the NFT Space, she can finally have a bright future ahead of her.

3/ SuperRare:

There are only 6 items being listed on this marketplace.

They're all really chaotic, crazy and traumatizing.
Combined with the colors that the artist decided to use, these pieces are really something else compared to the rest of the NFT Space. https://t.co/5ec2azCE9F

1/ Foundation:

Foundation is the home for 206 unique pieces, in which the main subjects seem to always be a girl, suffering through different events.

I'm actually surprised by how much these were being sold at, they should be a lot higher. https://t.co/voBt0jMQkW

Arts can be the most effective way to deliver a story, to share sad, traumatizing story to other people.

In this case, NFT arts even helped Haning to deliver her story to a bigger range of audience, through many of her collections:

For example, the piece below, if I'm not wrong, was based on an event of sexual harassment.
